<item>
            <title>[FLINK-8002] Incorrect join window boundaries for LESS_THAN and GREATER_THAN predicates</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/FLINK-8002</link>
                <project id="12315522" key="FLINK">Flink</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The boundaries of LESS_THAN and GREATER_THAN predicates are not correctly computed if the time attribute of the right table is referenced on the left side of the join predicate.&lt;br/&gt;
Instead of adding (subtracting) 1 millisecond, 1 millisecond is subtracted (added). &lt;br/&gt;
Hence, the boundary is off-by-2.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
